{2000}{}{I'm Ronnie. What can I do for you?}
{2010}{}{Just wondering if you can tell me anything about Junktown.}
{2020}{}{An old friend of yours, Mick, wants to put together a band. You in?}
{2030}{}{Mick sent me. He wants to save the wasteland through song, and you're the man he needs.}
