{7010}{}{Well can you tell me anything about the east? Like where did you come from?}
{8000}{}{New Vegas. Let me tell you, the place is a hellhole. If you ever head out that way, don't let the flashy lights draw you in. I used to play music out there, but got into some gambling problems. Started borrowing money, sure I was gonna win big. Before I knew it though, they were harassing me for the money. Money I couldn't pay back.}
{8010}{}{So you came here?}
